---
const values = [
  {
    title: "Private, not crowded",
    description: "Every route is framed around private timing, direct communication, and guest comfort.",
  },
  {
    title: "Premium, not complicated",
    description: "The website stays simple: choose the service, send details, and confirm through WhatsApp.",
  },
  {
    title: "Local, not generic",
    description: "The structure supports island-aware route decisions for transfers, tours, and custom stops.",
  },
];
---

<section class="container-page section-padding">
  <div class="grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] lg:items-start">
    <div>
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#e2e8f0]/60">Our positioning</p>
      <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight text-[#e2e8f0] sm:text-4xl">
        A travel service foundation shaped for premium guests.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-400 sm:text-base">
        This page keeps the brand story concise and operational. It is ready for real business copy later,
        while already communicating private driver confidence, island familiarity, and premium route handling.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid gap-4">
      {values.map((item) => (
        <article class="rounded-[8px] border border-white/10 bg-[#111827]/72 p-5 shadow-[0_18px_55px_rgba(0,0,0,0.22)]">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#e2e8f0]">{item.title}</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400">{item.description}</p>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
